            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="0"/>
                <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="line"/> <lb n="1"/><supplied reason="lost">Cl</supplied>audio A<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> proconsuli p<supplied reason="lost">rovinci</supplied>ae <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">Afr</supplied>icae omnium virtutum <lb n="4"/>viro innocentis integri<lb break="no" n="5"/>tatis vicoratae lenitatis <lb n="6"/>sublimis moderation<supplied reason="lost">i</supplied>s <lb n="7"/>laudavilis <note>sic</note> iustitiae <lb n="8"/>Lepcimagnenses ex de<lb break="no" n="9"/>creto ordinis patrono <lb n="10"/>perpetuo
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): AE 1957, 0235: Z. 2: [ex] proconsule. (B): Tantillo - Bigi, Nr. 36: Z. 11: spl(endissimi). Buchstabenhöhe: IRT 522: 3.5; IRT 610: 4.5; IRT 477: 4. Datierung: IRT 522: 290-294; IRT 610: 321-360; IRT 477: 379-395. Interpunktion: IRT 522: hedera; IRT 477: Palmette. The base has been used four times: first text erased, then IRT 522, then IRT 610 and last IRT 477 on the erased earlier text. Inschriftträger: column pedestal reused as statue base.</p>
            </div>
